{
  "name": "偽裝刺青 Masquerade Tattoo",
  "type": "equipment",
  "img": "icons/tools/scribal/burnisher-tooth.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"wordsection1\">覆蓋區域：一隻手，一隻腳或者一條肢體的四分之一</p><p class=\"wordsection1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">該魔法刺青用一根特殊的針製作，顯現為你所想要的樣子。</span> <br /><em><strong>刺青同調。</strong></em> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">同調此物品時，你需要將針持握，並抵在你想要讓刺</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">青出現</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的那處面板上。當同調完成時，針頭會化為墨水再變成刺青。若你與刺青的同調結束，刺青會消失，針頭會再次出現在你的位置中。</span> <br /><em><strong>液態油墨。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">作為一個附贈動作，你可以將刺青變為任意顏色或圖紋，並移動到你面板上的任意區域。無論</span><span class=\"GramE\">其有著</span>什麼形態，它看起來總是一個刺青。它的尺寸最小可為一枚銅幣，大則可 <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">覆蓋</span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">你的全身。</span> <br /><em><strong>易容自我。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">作為一個動作，你可以使用刺青施展</span> <em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.ju3LXSi72l6vso3l]{易容術 Disguise Self}</em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">法術（識破</span>DC13<span> </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">）。使用刺青施展這道法術后，直到下次黎明前，不能再次用刺青施展。</span></p></div>",
